  • java.lang.Object

  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class MacroHandler
extends Object
    Extracts macros from input strings and calls registered expanders to handle their input.

    Deprecated: Use StringWithMacros in constructor args and StringWithMacrosConverter instead.
